## TITLE('Biochemistry: Enzyme Kinetics Simulation')
## DESCRIPTION
## Interactive canvas-based enzyme simulation showing amylase and maltase
## catalyzed reactions. Students manipulate starting concentrations and answer
## multiple-choice questions about enzyme mechanisms.
## ENDDESCRIPTION
## KEYWORDS('enzymes','kinetics','amylase','maltase','substrate','catalyst','simulation')
## DBsubject('Biochemistry')
## DBchapter('Enzymes')
## DBsection('Kinetics')
## Level(2)
## Date('2026-02-26')
## Author('Dr. Neil R. Voss')
## Institution('Roosevelt University')
## Language(en)
# https://github.com/vosslab
#
# Derived from the Enzyme Simulation by Jolene Pappas / Biology Simulations LLC.
# Original: https://www.biologysimulations.com/enzymes
# Original simulation built with Phaser 3 and Plotly.js.
# Copyright 2026 Biology Simulations LLC.
